---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="Adam Parker - Founder, Rank4AI | AI Search Visibility" description="Adam Parker is the founder of Rank4AI, a UK AI search agency. Creator of The Five Signal Model. Over 15 years across commercial strategy, product.">

<article class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'About', href: '/about/' },
      { label: 'Team', href: '/about/team/' },
      { label: 'Adam Parker' }
    ]} />

    <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-8 mt-6">
      <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-teal text-text-light flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold flex-shrink-0">AP</div>
      <div>
        <h1 class="!text-3xl mb-1">Adam Parker</h1>
        <p class="text-accent font-medium">Founder, Rank4AI</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">Background</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Adam is the founder of Rank4AI, a UK AI search agency focused on improving visibility and recommendation likelihood across ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot and Google AI.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Over 15 years across commercial strategy, product, technology alignment and marketing. Old school commercial thinking applied to new school environments.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">The Five Signal Model</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Adam created <a href="/about/five-signal-framework/" class="link">The Five Signal Model</a> for AI search visibility: Identity Clarity, Subject Authority, Meaning Architecture, Ecosystem Validation, and Signal Consistency. The methodology and framework behind how AI systems evaluate whether a business is worth recommending.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">Approach</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">No tricks. No trends. Focused entirely on building trust with AI search platforms. Building genuine brand equity through solid identity, clear authority, structured architecture, consistent ecosystems and stable signals.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Boutique agency. No SaaS products. No juniors. No handoffs. Just hands-on work with every client. We do not do work you cannot understand. If something does not make sense, we explain it.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">Research</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Adam has audited over 1,400 UK businesses for AI search visibility, producing original research data that no other agency has published. This research underpins The Five Signal Model and Rank4AI's methodology.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">Company</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Rank4AI Ltd is registered in England and Wales. Company number 16584507. Based in Colchester, Essex. Adam works directly with every client.</p>

    <div class="mt-10 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Connect</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/adamparkerrank4ai/" class="link text-sm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="https://x.com/rank4ai" class="link text-sm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X / Twitter</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="link text-sm">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        <a href="/about/team/jimmy-connoley/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Jimmy Connoley</span></a>
        <a href="/about/five-signal-framework/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Five Signal Model</span></a>
        <a href="/research/methodology/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Our Methodology</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>

<!-- Person Schema -->
<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
